<http://data.org/RA63> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://guia.org/LearningResult> .
<http://data.org/RA63> <https://guia.org/learningResultCode> "RA63" .
<http://data.org/RA63> <https://guia.org/learningResultDescription> "RA67"@es .
# 
# http://data.org/RA73
<http://data.org/RA73> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<http://data.org/RA73> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://guia.org/LearningResult> .
<http://data.org/RA73> <https://guia.org/learningResultCode> "RA73" .
<http://data.org/RA73> <https://guia.org/learningResultDescription> "Analizar y diseñar sociedades de agentes que simulen comportamientos inteligentes"@es .
# 
# http://data.org/615001035
<http://data.org/615001035> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
